{"tid":105440,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩番鄉下, 租左部大眾朗逸揸","createTime":"2017-02-03T01:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-06T10:13:03.000Z","uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ace2512a3f50fd7407f0fce1f88046d6dd0f0480","tid":105440,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:40:13.000Z","msg":"係一嗨租車<br />\n初一福建拎車<br />\n初四還車, 加埋免墊底費, 要成1400人仔<br />\n油費都係得200人仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6gf7p1sn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6gf7p1sn&h=e1b620e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/y5mbwsnk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fy5mbwsnk&h=aeedce2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n車頭蓋一開, 間車以為跌過落屎坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mvce2wfq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmvce2wfq&h=853ef3be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n還車先發覺前bumper有條痕<br />\n可能因為泊鄉村街邊, 俾d電單車挖到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好彩唔駛賠, 租車公司條友教我要同CS講係我自己唔小心挖到.... 打110公安叫我自己搵保險公司....  <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/01lag75y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F01lag75y&h=d533efe7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c00eecaaeb274b1259569028b76be2c58adb1bdd","tid":105440,"uid":33826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:44:55.000Z","msg":"點解可以咁多塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a8d35a408f8fc7d8da1e1ad422ff6127690a76","tid":105440,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:47:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解可以咁多塵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n上面鄉下地方d沙塵真係好勁<img