.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a4cf5cf99586d4fc6fbd2d68ed145a47c300060","tid":105440,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n36<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想問未夠25係咪好貴保<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一般租車, 30歲以下會貴d, 保險多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d655e41cc8e37b03c39cf8240bbc9e45b1423b8","tid":105440,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T03:10:36.000Z","msg":"德原朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/14.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"188c55a17254b125c09f57b554c9516a76c8ca07","tid":105440,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T06:54:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e407033dd8ef24f40b96c03b3c40a29bb3f7f5ea","tid":105440,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>岩岩先係河源玩完返黎, 家下坐係東莞食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己揸車??<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係, 去左2個地方都係河源, 無咩野玩, 相入面個係假溫泉渡假區, 入面好大仲開發緊, 住喜來登1千人仔左右一晚, 包假溫泉, 早餐, 裡面仲有機動遊戲, 不過無咩興趣, 玩呢D都係去返長隆好D. 酒店幾靚, 不過玩同食就無咩, 之後去左紫金浸真溫泉, 酒店都OK, 週圍都好多野食同平好多, 不過酒店就貴多8舊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9efd18d5b508d045ddaf13a715a54ad15417caf","tid":105440,"uid":28001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T03:32:41.000Z","msg":"大眾OK的.<br />\n<br />\n公司車坐緊Passat 加長版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2af28c4fb08c1552f47dd24de901a2b8dedf1eb3","tid":105440,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-0